{"title":"呜呜~~ 我的第一次就这么没了","uid":"5d8d7e50b2cf44097e19612762ff2845","slug":"hello-world","date":"2021-11-19T09:35:21.000Z","updated":"2022-01-26T08:34:17.282Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://source.unsplash.com/PUvPZckRnOg/1200x628","content":"<p>最近这几天，受到一个学生的引诱，俺也觉得hexo的博客挺好看的，所以我也就搞了一个，原本其他人的教程感觉很是简单，六年级的小伙子都能搞出来，那岂不是对我来说很简单了，啊哈哈！但是在成功的路上总是孤单的、并且也是很无趣的。</p>\n<p>根据教程我把我的github都布置好了，然后就在选择炫酷的主题让我挠头了一天！！！！！！</p>\n<p>下面我将把我的九九八十一难 呈现给在座的你。。。。。</p>\n<p><b>下面正式从零开始搭建年轻人的第一个网站：</b></p>\n<h2 id=\"免费搭建博客\"><a href=\"#免费搭建博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"免费搭建博客\"></a>免费搭建博客</h2><h3 id=\"目录\"><a href=\"#目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"目录\"></a>目录</h3><ul>\n<li><p><b>GitHub创建个人仓库</b></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><b>安装Git</b></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><b>安装Node.js</b></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><b>安装Hexo</b></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><b>推送网站</b></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"GitHub创建个人仓库\"><a href=\"#GitHub创建个人仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GitHub创建个人仓库\"></a>GitHub创建个人仓库</h3><p>Hexo 5.4+<br>Yarn or NPM installed</p>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装指南\"><a href=\"#安装指南\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装指南\"></a>安装指南</h3><h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo server<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo generate<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo deploy<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"快速上手\"><a href=\"#快速上手\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速上手\"></a>快速上手</h2>","text":"最近这几天，受到一个学生的引诱，俺也觉得hexo的博客挺好看的，所以我也就搞了一个，原本其他人的教程感觉很是简单，六年级的小伙子都能搞出来，那岂不是对我来说很简单了，啊哈哈！但是在成功的路上总是孤单的、并且也是很无趣的。 根据教程我把我的github都布置好了，然后就在选择炫酷的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":492,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo Aurora","slug":"Hexo-Aurora","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo-Aurora.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">免费搭建博客</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">目录</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#GitHub%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">GitHub创建个人仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装指南</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Run-server\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Run server</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Generate-static-files\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Generate static files</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Deploy to remote site